<div style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #111; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">You're now a provider on OllaZen!</h1>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Hi <%= @user.name.presence || 'there' %>!</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Your account has been upgraded to a provider account. Your business <strong><%= @business_name %></strong> is now set up on OllaZen.</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">You can now manage your business, add services, and accept bookings from your provider dashboard.</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Once our team has reviewed your profile, your listing will be visible to customers. We'll notify you when you're approved.</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">— The OllaZen team</p>
</div>
